            üìä Seasonal Pattern Analysis
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6 max-w-3xl text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">
            Creativity and complexity by month. Creativity = avg_word_count √ó avg_complexity.
            Formula: creativity(month) = mean(word_count for posts in month) √ó mean(complexity for
            posts in month)
          </p>
